    </div>
  <p>GOARCH is the running program&#39;s architecture target:
one of 386, amd64, arm, s390x, and so on.
</p>

    <div class="Documentation-declaration">
      <span class="Documentation-declarationLink"><a class="Documentation-source" href="https://cs.opensource.google/go/go/+/go1.18.3:src/runtime/extern.go;l=271">View Source</a></span>
      <pre><span id="GOOS" data-kind="constant">const GOOS <a href="/builtin#string">string</a> = <a href="/internal/goos">goos</a>.<a href="/internal/goos#GOOS">GOOS</a></span></pre>
