        </div><div class="Documentation-function">
	  
  
  
    <h4 tabindex="-1" id="Callers" data-kind="function" class="Documentation-functionHeader">
      <span>func <a class="Documentation-source" href="https://cs.opensource.google/go/go/+/go1.18.3:src/runtime/extern.go;l=228">Callers</a> <a class="Documentation-idLink" href="#Callers">Â¶</a></span>
